snippet.title: Assassin's Creed 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: The wait is finally over, it is time once again to follow the creed this time living the life of Ezio Auditore, a young man whose life will be changed by unforseen events which will make him seek revenge and become a master Assassin.
